# New England Cohort Dataset

## General Information

All participants included in this repository had MR images from at least two timepoints that passed the QC standards for the referenced manuscript. Additional timepoints were included regardless of QC status.

### Developmental Timepoints

- **80 subjects, 192 scans in total**
- `ses-01` = infant (~2–18 months); 62 participants
- `ses-02` = toddler (~16–26 months); 21 participants
- `ses-03` = pre-reading (~56–78 months / 4.6–6.5 years); 51 participants
- `ses-04` = beginning reading (~73–101 months / 6–8.4 years); 34 participants
- `ses-05` = emergent reading (~87–121 months / 7–10 years); 24 participants

